Data Sources:

1. Randolph Glacier Inventory (RGI)
   - Source: GLIMS/RGI Consortium
   - License: Open Database License (ODbL)
   - Citation: RGI Consortium (2017). Randolph Glacier Inventory – A Dataset of Global Glacier Outlines: Version 6.0

2. MODIS Albedo Data
   - Source: NASA Earthdata - MODIS MCD43A3
   - License: NASA Open Data Policy
   - Citation: Schaaf, C., & Wang, Z. (2015). MCD43A3 MODIS/Terra+Aqua BRDF/Albedo Daily L3 Global 500m SIN Grid V006

3. ArcGIS API for JavaScript
   - Source: Esri Inc.
